  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The hypothesis of this study is that tacrolimus reduces the proteinuria in adult patient with
      minimal change nephritic syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A pilot study for comparative clinical trial on the therapeutic effect of tacrolimus (Prograf
      cap®) in adult patient with minimal change nephritic syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
